---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Archivio
description: Archivio delle storie seed del 22 marzo 2026.
---
<section class="page">
  <header class="hero hero-compact">
    <p class="eyebrow">Archivio</p>
    <h1>Tutte le storie</h1>
    <p class="lead">La raccolta completa degli articoli derivati dalla pagina originale, ordinati per data e categoria.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="archive-list">
    {% for article in collections.articles %}
    <article class="card archive-item">
      <p class="eyebrow">{{ article.data.categoryName }} · {{ article.date | displayDate }}</p>
      <h3><a href="{{ article.url | url }}">{{ article.data.title }}</a></h3>
      <p>{{ article.data.excerpt }}</p>
      <div class="story-meta">
        {% for source in article.data.sources %}
        <span class="tag">{{ source }}</span>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </section>
</section>
